# Unique Requirements & Stretch Challenges

This project meets the following requirements:
- Demonstrates core C++ features:
1.variables
2.expressions
3.conditionals
4.loops
5.functions
6.classes

- Uses an STL data structure

Stretch challenges include:
- Adding file I/O for saving and loading tasks
- Using inheritance with virtual functions
- Managing objects with new and delete

